      <sop.para>
        <text><emphasis style="italic">New section 173(1)</emphasis>: to omit <amend.in quote="1">section 13A(2) of the Evidence Act 1908</amend.in> (line 30 on page 91) and substitute <amend.in quote="1">section 108 of the Evidence Act 2006</amend.in>.</text>
