      </sop.para>
      <sop.para>
        <text><emphasis style="italic">New section 179</emphasis>: to omit <amend.in quote="1">section 13A(6)(d) of the Evidence Act 1908</amend.in> (lines 12 and 13 on page 95) and substitute <amend.in quote="1">section 109(1)(d) of the Evidence Act 2006</amend.in>.</text>
      </sop.para>
